              "WarningsOrContraIndicationDescription": [
                {
                  "LanguageCode": "en",
                  "Value": "If you have sensitive skin or allergic hypersensitivity, first check the skin reaction on a smaller area of skin. Do not apply the sport tape too tightly so as not to restrict the blood supply. If you experience a numb or tingling sensation, remove or loosen the tape immediately. Do not wear while sleeping. Change the tape daily. Carefully remove the tape lengthways from the skin to avoid skin damage. Use with caution. If you tape regularly or if you have sensitive skin, use an under-tape first. Use the sports tape on intact skin. Keep out of the reach of children. Inform the manufacturer and the competent authority of any serious incidents."
                }
